results.name: a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n} mobius(binomial(n,k)).
example: a(4)=3 because mobius(1) + mobius(4) + mobius(6) + mobius(4) + mobius(1) = 1 + 0 + 1 + 0 + 1 = 3.
